  <scopecontent id="aspace_90700326db5e7c5bf3d811a8e564d849">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Research collection of photographic slides, publications, and notes on Ragamala painting. Materials were gathered while Ebeling was conducting research for his book Ragamala Painting, published in 1973.</p>  </scopecontent>
